      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and would make a solid choice for someone willing to put in a little work. The engine starts and runs, though it could benefit from a comprehensive tune-up, and the transmission is functional but shows its age with occasional stiff shifts. Cosmetically, there are visible blemishes including some minor dents and interior wear consistent with its history. It's a reliable enough driver for now, but it will eventually need some maintenance to bring it back to its best state.",
